Package grave_escape.levels.Level2

Class Level2Normal

java.lang.Object
grave_escape.levels.Level
grave_escape.levels.Level2.Level2Normal
public class Level2Normal extends Level
Represents the normal version of Level 2. This class extends the Level class and initializes specific configurations such as enemies, objectives, walls, starting position, and exit position for normal difficulty of Level 2.
